If we desire a stable and thriving democracy, parties must be at the forefront of providing good leadership. 
It is time we embarked of a serious civic education programme. We can’t achieve democracy with undemocratic citizens. 
Mr Otiato is a political scientist. brunootiato1@gmail.com. The DP's ambition to take over from his boss after the 2022 elections is a road with two paths. The decision is a blow to two aspirants who had applied to the party for sponsorship to contest the seat. This shift of focus is so dire that the World Health Organization now warns that by the end of 2020, more people will have died of malaria than Covid-19.